# Red Dragon

A Python package that awakens the red dragon!

## Installation

```bash
pip install red-dragon
```

## Usage

After installation, simply run:

```bash
red-dragon
```

## Description

This package displays a beautiful ASCII art dragon when you run the `red-dragon` command.

